# Generate Chat Completion

# Description

Given a prompt and other inputs, generate a chat completion.

# Project compatibility

Windows | Cross-platform

# Configuration

* 
* Model identifier - The identifier of the model used for the completion. Select a model from the dropdown list.
* Prompt text - Input to use for the chat completion request. This field supports String type input.









* Chat Completion - Automatically generated output variable.
* Text - Content from the vendor.
